  "calendarNotes": "Wake County Public School System begins the 2026–2027 school year on August 24, 2026, following a teacher workday week August 17–21. Thanksgiving break runs November 25–27. Winter break runs December 21, 2026 through January 1, 2027; school reopens January 4. Good Friday (March 26) is a school holiday. Spring Break runs March 29 – April 2, 2027, followed by a teacher workday on April 5. The school year ends June 9, 2027."
